<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 06:18:24 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>罗素：中国降息未能重振铁矿石和铜矿</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/chinas-rate-cuts-fail-revive-iron-ore-copper-russell-2024-07-23/</link><description>中国11个月来首次下调主要短期和长期利率，引起了通常被认为是最大受益者的大宗商品的明显反应。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 05:51:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/chinas-rate-cuts-fail-revive-iron-ore-copper-russell-2024-07-23/</guid></item><item><title>美国关税威胁迫在眉睫，数字税收谈判成为 G20 焦点</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/digital-tax-talks-g20-spotlight-us-tariff-threat-looms-2024-07-23/</link><description>关于全球税收协议的谈判在 6 月 30 日截止日期之后仍在继续，各国政府目前正在等待本周举行的 20 国集团财长会议，以期在一项陷入僵局的大型跨国公司重新分配征税权的计划上取得进展。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 05:10:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/digital-tax-talks-g20-spotlight-us-tariff-threat-looms-2024-07-23/</guid></item><item><title>Windrose计划在美国组装卡车，这是中国电动汽车公司罕见的举动</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/windrose-plans-truck-assembly-us-rare-move-by-chinese-ev-firm-2024-07-23/</link><description>中国电动卡车初创公司Windrose创始人兼首席执行官韩文在接受采访时表示，该公司计划在美国设立一家半挂卡车组装厂，从2025年起在美国交付，直接挑战特斯拉在本土市场的地位。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 05:07:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/windrose-plans-truck-assembly-us-rare-move-by-chinese-ev-firm-2024-07-23/</guid></item><item><title>随着市场复苏，中国企业发行创纪录的 140 亿美元可转换债券</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/china-firms-issue-record-14-bln-convertible-bonds-market-revives-2024-07-23/</link><description>今年迄今为止，中国顶尖企业已通过离岸可转换债券筹集了创纪录的 140 亿美元资金，以在利率居高不下的情况下实现未来融资需求的多元化。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 04:50:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/china-firms-issue-record-14-bln-convertible-bonds-market-revives-2024-07-23/</guid></item><item><title>巴勒斯坦各派在中国会谈后签署结束分裂宣言</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/hamas-fatah-meet-with-media-china-after-reconciliation-talks-2024-07-23/</link><description>据中国官方媒体报道，巴勒斯坦各派别周二上午在中国签署《北京宣言》，同意结束分裂并加强巴勒斯坦团结。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 03:44:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/hamas-fatah-meet-with-media-china-after-reconciliation-talks-2024-07-23/</guid></item><item><title>上半年城镇新增就业698万人</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-adds-698-mln-urban-new-jobs-first-half-year-2024-07-23/</link><description>据人力资源部称，中国周二表示，今年上半年城镇新增就业人员698万人。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 02:51:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-adds-698-mln-urban-new-jobs-first-half-year-2024-07-23/</guid></item><item><title>官方媒体称中国调整贷款抵押品将缓解“资产荒”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/chinas-loan-collateral-tweak-will-ease-asset-famine-state-media-says-2024-07-23/</link><description>官方媒体周二援引消息人士的话说，中国央行决定降低中期贷款抵押要求，将缓解债券市场的“资产荒”压力。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 02:25:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/chinas-loan-collateral-tweak-will-ease-asset-famine-state-media-says-2024-07-23/</guid></item><item><title>尽管中美关系日益紧张，制药巨头仍将目光投向中国寻求交易</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/drug-giants-eye-china-deals-despite-growing-sino-us-tensions-2024-07-23/</link><description>行业高管和投资银行家表示，一些全球最大的制药商并未因中美紧张局势加剧而望而却步，正在中国寻找交易，以补充药品管道并提高其在全球第二大制药市场的影响力。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 02:17:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/drug-giants-eye-china-deals-despite-growing-sino-us-tensions-2024-07-23/</guid></item><item><title>芯片股在巨额盈利之前反弹</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-07-23/</link><description>亚洲股市周二企稳，半导体股反弹，打破了昂贵的连跌势头，而中国黯淡的需求前景拖累了大宗商品价格，投资者将注意力转向美国财报和数据。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 01:56:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-07-23/</guid></item><item><title>台风“高美”逼近台湾，台湾缩减年度军事演习</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-curtails-annual-war-games-typhoon-gaemi-barrels-towards-island-2024-07-23/</link><description>由于台风“高美”猛冲台湾，台湾周二缩减了一年一度的汉光军事演习，鉴于台风“高美”袭击海岸时预计将出现强风和暴雨，台湾政府发布了陆地警告。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 01:55:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-curtails-annual-war-games-typhoon-gaemi-barrels-towards-island-2024-07-23/</guid></item><item><title>五角大楼表示，俄罗斯和中国在北极的合作不断加强</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/growing-cooperation-between-russia-china-arctic-pentagon-says-2024-07-23/</link><description>美国军方周一在发布北极地区战略时表示，俄罗斯和中国在北极地区的合作日益增多，这可能会影响地区稳定。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 01:44:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/growing-cooperation-between-russia-china-arctic-pentagon-says-2024-07-23/</guid></item><item><title>澳元、新西兰元因中国降息而苦苦挣扎；日元上涨</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/aussie-kiwi-dollars-struggle-chinas-rate-cuts-dollar-adrift-2024-07-23/</link><description>在中国下调多项关键利率后，澳元和新西兰元周二努力重新站稳脚跟，而日元在日本央行(BOJ)月底政策会议之前上涨。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 01:01:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/aussie-kiwi-dollars-struggle-chinas-rate-cuts-dollar-adrift-2024-07-23/</guid></item><item><title>早间竞价：随着拜登出局，股市反弹，选举局势混乱</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-2024-07-22/</link><description>奥尔登·本特利 (Alden Bentley) 展望亚洲市场未来一天。</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Jul 2024 21:50:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-2024-07-22/</guid></item><item><title>伯克希尔哈撒韦公司将比亚迪股份减持至5%以下</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/berkshire-hathaway-cuts-stake-chinas-byd-below-5-2024-07-22/</link><description>沃伦·巴菲特的伯克希尔·哈撒韦公司将其在比亚迪的股份降至 5% 以下，这可能是伯克希尔哈撒韦公司最后一次披露中国最大电动汽车生产商的股票销售情况。</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Jul 2024 14:04:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/berkshire-hathaway-cuts-stake-chinas-byd-below-5-2024-07-22/</guid></item><item><title>油轮丑闻后，中国卡车和食品制造商试图重新赢得消费者信任</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinese-truck-food-makers-attempt-regain-consumer-trust-after-tanker-scandal-2024-07-22/</link><description>中国的卡车制造商周一发布了运载食用油的车辆的安全标准，在有关运输食用油的油罐车的报道重新引发人们对食品污染的担忧后，各公司试图重新获得消费者的信任。</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Jul 2024 13:05:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinese-truck-food-makers-attempt-regain-consumer-trust-after-tanker-scandal-2024-07-22/</guid></item></channel></rss>